analysis.Summary: Vue component that renders a double-check SVG icon, with a configurable fill color.
analysis.Purpose: Provide a reusable double-check icon for navigation or status indicators in the UI.

Components.name: IconDoubleCheck
Components.role: Renders the SVG element with two check‚Äêmark paths and accepts a fill color prop.

Notes: No <style> block is defined; styling is entirely via the SVG and prop.
The `fill` prop default is defined as an object ({ position: 'rgb(var(--black))' }) instead of a string, which may be unintended.
The component is stateless and purely presentational.
